      "question": "Given the goal of KG construction, please include metrics and analysis on the recall and comprehensive coverage of the extracted knowledge, beyond just precision or acceptance rate.",
      "motivation": "For KG construction, discovering a wide range of correct knowledge (high recall) is as important as ensuring correctness. A method with high precision but low coverage for novel relations might have limited practical value."
    },
    {
      "question": "For improved reproducibility, could the authors specify the exact API parameters (e.g., temperature, top-k, number of generations) used for GPT-3 during prompt generation? Would it be possible to provide a small set of example generated prompts or a pseudo-code for their filtering process?",
      "motivation": "Reliance on a proprietary model like GPT-3, coupled with unspecified generation and filtering parameters, makes independent replication of results practically impossible, hindering scientific validation."
    }
  ],
